facts.text: On October 31, 1950, appellant made an application under s. 78 of the Tenancy Act to the Tahsildar, Merta, for rent from tenants in Khakharki.

anchor.surface_text: On October 31, 1950, the appellant who had some difficulty in realising the rent from his tenants in village Khakharki, made an application under s. 78 of the Tenancy Act to the Tahsildar, Merta, within which the village Khakharki was situate.

facts.text: On March 9, 1951, appellant filed application under s. 85 to Collector, Nagaur, for recovery of 1950-51 rents from Khakharki tenants as arrears of land revenue.
